  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/03/esa-leaf-accoustic-rocket-test-facility/\"><img alt=\"NOORDWIJK - ESA ESTEC Noordwijk. - FOTO GUUS SCHOONEWILLE\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/cca5bc038119e00f92dd95d2296ec647/large-european-acoustic-facility-speaker-2014-02-03-01.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n觉得自己的<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2008/10/12/mgm-reveals-specifications-extras-for-spinal-tap-on-blu-ray/\">音响</a>很威？敢跟欧洲太空总署旗下的 LEAF（Large European Acoustic Facility）比一比吗？他们有一堵宽 36 英尺、高 54 英尺（约 10 米和 16 米）的音墙，可以模拟出火箭发射时的音效。具体来说，它能通过将氮气注入喇叭产生出 154 分贝的声响，这差不多就是几架喷气机同时在你耳边起飞的感觉，一不小心会出人命的。据悉研究者是希望通过这套系统来对卫星进行压力测试，确保它们在火箭上不会出什么问题。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/03/esa-leaf-accoustic-rocket-test-facility/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://io9.com/this-sound-system-is-so-powerful-no-human-could-survive-1512501017\" target=\"_blank\">io9</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.esa.int/spaceinimages/Images/2014/01/Large_European_Acoustic_Facility\" target=\"_blank\">ESA</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/03/esa-leaf-accoustic-rocket-test-facility/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20821923/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/03/esa-leaf-accoustic-rocket-test-facility/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
